HWACOM SYSTEMS I said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 57.28% to NT$111,772,000 from NT$261,613,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2011           4/2010
Sales            111,772          261,613    
YOY%             -57.28%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            566,726          675,658    
YOY%             -16.12% 
=================================================================
 